  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supporting  the Finance &amp; Admin department in daily accounting work</li>\n  <li>Perform accounting duties &amp; administrative support – filling, data entry etc</li>\n  <li>Prepare Bank Reconciliations</li>\n  <li>Handle accounts payable &amp; accounts receivable</li>\n  <li>Enter accurate and timely data into the accounting system</li>\n  <li>Preparation of monthly report and ensure timely closing of monthly accounts</li>\n  <li>All other adhoc admin / accounting duties assigned from time to time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficiency  in Ms Excel, Words</li>\n  <li>Hardworking  &amp; fast learner</li>\n  <li>At least 3  years of experience in accounting &amp; finance</li>\n  <li>Strong  understanding of accounting principles</li>\n  <li>Ability to  work independently with a high degree of accuracy and efficiency</li>\n  <li>Diploma in Accountancy or equivalent</li>\n</ul>",
